{"tid":1167232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［已還押半年］郭紹傑續還押至六月底再訊","createTime":"2019-05-23T02:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-23T02:26:25.000Z","uid":50386,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ec4b52ddd6fee07950fdff14928b234edda8b83c","tid":1167232,"uid":50386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:10:37.000Z","msg":"保釣行動委員會成員郭紹傑及嚴敏華，去年12月在日本靖國神社外焚燒日本戰犯東條英機道具神主牌，遭當地警方拘捕，被控非法進入他人建築物罪，案件昨日在東京地方裁判所開審，控方在庭上播放二人在靖國神社外焚燒道具神主牌之片段，法官將案押至6月21日再訊。  <br />\n<br />\n郭紹傑在庭上抗議，要求法官解釋為何不准二人保釋，或加快審訊程序，又指已將事件交由律師及家人，向聯合國投訴，法官回覆指不准保釋是早前的決定，且法庭已加快審訊程序。  <br />\n<br />\n郭紹傑質疑，為何自己只是舉牌兩分鐘，便要被拘留半年，如按現時審訊進度，估計審結時二人已被囚一年<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁就留響日本留左半年<br />\n好多人恨都恨唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aacdbf55269741bfd0b05816543f14e0900fdcf","tid":1167232,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:11:45.000Z","msg":"最高幾多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a7b9226e62bd53664bedc5f35e2fd0556e9ae5","tid":1167232,"uid":31837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"乖啦，仲喺個庭度嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2ed5a093ae2dc5dcaaabcde1590665f8212d6d","tid":1167232,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"日日食國產食物 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f2576ad8aa87ef054d1dbf4063cbf3c600b978","tid":1167232,"uid":60408,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:14:56.000Z","msg":"放完火問點解自己舉牌比人拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f783433ef9797ff825a3a8919419ffdb15f5f5ec","tid":1167232,"uid":74043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-23T02:15:27.000Z","msg":"報應"},{"pid":"ed8cdeda2c1cf2de451474e40b394e3702a8be07","tid":1167232,"uid":22590,"like":3,"dislike":